MALE DRIVER (LONE OCCUPANT) WAS TRANSPORTED TO HOSPITAL WI TH NON-LIFE THREATENING INJURIES. ALCOHOL WAS DETECTED ON DRIVER & HE WAS CITED FOR FAILURE TO YIELD .
